CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783685999
OL,3,CBeavers among 'vulnerable' species
OL,4,Cthat wildlife trust pledges to help
OL,5,Crecover
OL,7,FThey include securing the future of
OL,8,Fwild beavers at the River Stour and
OL,9,Ffinding new ways to grow populations
OL,10,Fof the heath fritillary butterfly in
OL,11,Fthe Blean - one of the UK's largest
OL,12,Fareas of ancient woodland.
OL,14,FThe government has hailed the project
OL,15,Fas the "largest-ever investment in
OL,16,Fspecies recovery".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783685999
OL,3,CBeavers among 'vulnerable' species
OL,4,Cthat wildlife trust pledges to help
OL,5,Crecover
OL,7,FThe trust, in collaboration with a
OL,8,Frange of partner organisations, will
OL,9,Flook to strengthen the genetic
OL,10,Fdiversity and long-term resilience of
OL,11,Fthe River Stour's beaver population -
OL,12,Fwhich is the biggest in England.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
