OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783685999
OL,3,CBeavers among 'vulnerable' species
OL,4,Cthat wildlife trust pledges to help
OL,5,Crecover
OL,7,FIt says this will be done through
OL,8,F"carefully managed wild releases,
OL,9,Fwhile creating a nationally
OL,10,Fsignificant model for beaver
OL,11,Fcoexistence".
OL,13,FSome of the UK's rarest woodland
OL,14,Finvertebrates and butterflies,
OL,15,Fmeanwhile, call the Blean their home.
OL,17,FTo better understand their
OL,18,Fdistribution and habitat needs,
OL,19,Fsurveys will be conducted on six
OL,20,Fnationally scarce species.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
