OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783685999
OL,3,CBeavers among 'vulnerable' species
OL,4,Cthat wildlife trust pledges to help
OL,5,Crecover
OL,7,FConservationists will also investigate
OL,8,Fwhy populations of the heath
OL,9,Ffritillary butterfly are in decline in
OL,10,Fsome areas and test different ways of
OL,11,Fmanaging the woodland.
OL,13,FPaul Hadaway, Director of Conservation
OL,14,Fand Engagement at Kent Wildlife Trust,
OL,15,Fsaid the investment "recognises just
OL,16,Fhow important Kent is for some of
OL,17,FEngland's most at-risk wildlife".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
