PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783685999
OL,3,CBeavers among 'vulnerable' species
OL,4,Cthat wildlife trust pledges to help
OL,5,Crecover
OL,7,FHe added: "It gives us the opportunity
OL,8,Fto strengthen our nationally important
OL,9,Fbeaver population, deepen our
OL,10,Funderstanding of some of England's
OL,11,Fleast known woodland invertebrates,
OL,12,Fand create the conditions for them to
OL,13,Frecover and thrive."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
